Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,開眼 萬花筒寫輪眼的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管前面的路有多麼黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都會勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.05,0:02:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管碰到什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都要得到力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經很晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺剛才好像有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,街上的燈…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明還沒到睡覺的時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 嬸嬸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:03:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動啊 動啊 動啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和媽媽怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的弟弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:05:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬花筒寫輪眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要給我看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼哥哥會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:07:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了測試我自己的器量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測試器量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為這個 把大家都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒謊 這不是哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.20,0:08:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以一直扮演你理想中的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了測試你的器量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.90,0:09:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你將來可能會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為我測試器量的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在討厭我 憎恨我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直期望能超越我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此 我才讓你活著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是為了我 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是萬花筒寫輪眼的開眼者之一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那需要特殊的條件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺掉自己最親密的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:10:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是關於昨晚\N跳入南賀河自殺的宇智波止水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒來聚會的另一個人就是止水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像將止水當成自己的親哥哥對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥殺了止水先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 我得到了這種能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南賀神社的正殿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右數第七塊榻榻米之下 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便是家族的秘密聚會地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面記載著宇智波一族的瞳術為何而生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是其真正的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你開眼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包含我在內 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:11:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌握萬花筒寫輪眼的就有三個人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有讓你活下去的意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本沒有被殺的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的弟弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想殺我 就憎恨 怨恨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後醜陋地活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不斷地逃啊逃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要苟延殘喘地活著便好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後有一天 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你擁有和我一樣的眼睛時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就來找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:11:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 據說只有這個孩子得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.10,0:12:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子好像還有個哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說行蹤不明了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到名門宇智波一族會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天來買什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 要去上學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才看到鼬了 真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是一流的忍者了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七歲就以第一名的成績從忍者學校畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十歲就升為了中忍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八歲就會使用寫輪眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子真是宇智波一族的驕傲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來了啊 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼總是只想著哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥是哥哥 你是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸總是很在乎你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南賀神社的正殿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右數第七塊榻榻米之下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便是家族的秘密聚會地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 就是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學後去不去點心鋪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去 不去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽很和藹 真是幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是讓我媽知道我買零食吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會很麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇智波一族好像都被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽爸爸說了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那傢伙活了下了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.30,0:18:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸總是會提到你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和媽媽說過些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想殺我 就憎恨 怨恨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了殺你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管前面的路多麼困難
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都會勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管碰到什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:18:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都要得到力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始 我就是一個復仇者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助現在身處黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在這裏停下的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就追不上佐助了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧次 你說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙現在身處黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然真想置我於死地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.60,0:19:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不是你的朋友了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們第七班一直以來所做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部毫無意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管碰到什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都要得到力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.00,0:20:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為如此 打倒你才有價值
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.40,0:20:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我沒弄懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我知道你真的想置我於死地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.45,0:22:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想置我於死地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.45,0:22:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在連你剛才說的話是真是假都分不清
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.45,0:22:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許只有我一廂情願地真正當你是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.65,0:22:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.08,0:22:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就太沒面子了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.55,0:23:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.85,0:23:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友
